		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Personally, I'm against adding a bunch of garbage around the ROM contents mainly because it makes it harder to extract them for the purpose of burning chips, as if people didn't already have enough trouble when doing that.
<br />
<br />UNIF sucked because of this. Extracting the ROMs should be a simple task, simple enough to be accomplished without the use of any tools. It took me a while to locate the ROMs inside a UNIF file the last time I needed to extract them.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
